---
title: Korean Inspired BBQ Night with Chicken & Halloumi Skewers, Sticky BBQ Sausages, Chips and Kimchi Style Slaw
description: Enjoy the best of the British summertime with a BBQ feast! Perfectly suited for cooking on your BBQ, this Korean Inspired BBQ Night can also be just as easily prepared in your oven.
